Package com.irurueta.navigation.indoor

Class RangingAndRssiReading<S extends RadioSource>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.irurueta.navigation.indoor.Reading<S>
      • com.irurueta.navigation.indoor.RangingAndRssiReading<S>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - a RadioSource type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RangingAndRssiReadingLocated
    public class RangingAndRssiReading<S extends RadioSource>
extends Reading<S>
    Contains a reading associated to a given radio source (e.e. WiFi access point or bluetooth beacon) containing signal strength and distance to associated access point.
